#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn51.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Cāpālavagga "
msgstr "1. At the Cāpāla Shrine "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Samattasutta "
msgstr "6. Completely "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn51.6:1.1"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samattaṃ iddhiṃ abhinipphādesuṃ, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, all the ascetics and brahmins in the past who have completely manifested psychic powers have done so by developing and cultivating the four bases of psychic power. "

msgctxt "sn51.6:1.2"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samattaṃ iddhiṃ abhinipphādessanti, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
msgstr "All the ascetics and brahmins in the future who will completely manifest psychic powers will do so by developing and cultivating the four bases of psychic power. "

msgctxt "sn51.6:1.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samattaṃ iddhiṃ abhinipphādenti, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
msgstr "All the ascetics and brahmins in the present who are completely manifesting psychic powers do so by developing and cultivating the four bases of psychic power. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn51.6:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn51.6:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.6:2.3"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe … "
msgstr "energy … "

msgctxt "sn51.6:2.4"
msgid "cittasamādhi … pe … "
msgstr "mental development … "

msgctxt "sn51.6:2.5"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. "
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.6:2.6"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samattaṃ iddhiṃ abhinipphādesuṃ, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
msgstr "All the ascetics and brahmins in the past who have completely manifested psychic powers have done so by developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power. "

msgctxt "sn51.6:2.7"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samattaṃ iddhiṃ abhinipphādessanti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
msgstr "All the ascetics and brahmins in the future who will completely manifest psychic powers will do so by developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power. "

msgctxt "sn51.6:2.8"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samattaṃ iddhiṃ abhinipphādenti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā”ti. "
msgstr "All the ascetics and brahmins in the present who are completely manifesting psychic powers do so by developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.6:2.9"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

